casebody.data:
No. 10-9138. Jason McKinley Ward, Petitioner v. Catherine Cortez Masto, Attorney General of Nevada, et al. 563 U.S. 958, 131 S. Ct. 2155,

179 L. Ed. 2d 933,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 3348. April 25, 2011.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
